{"tid":2370182,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"侵支持者問侵: 可摸以特赦我?","createTime":"2021-01-17T22:03:22.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-18T06:47:18.000Z","uid":105798,"like":11,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a7cfc8f4af152f6bca57efda096c17b5c481c664","tid":2370182,"uid":105798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T22:03:22.000Z","msg":"&ldquo;I would like a <span class=\"red\">pardon</span> from the president of the United States,&rdquo; said <span class=\"red\">Jenna Ryan</span>, a Texas real estate agent charged in the storming of the Capitol, in an interview with CBS News late last week. &ldquo;<span class=\"red\">I think that we all deserve a pardon</span>. I&rsquo;m facing a prison sentence. I think that I do not deserve that.&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u7hiYVP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu7hiYVP.jpg&h=55d05674&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAn attorney for Jacob Chansley (即係個個維京) &mdash; the man who entered the Capitol wearing horns and carrying a spear &mdash; said on CNN that his client also deserved a pardon, as he was only in the Capitol because he had &ldquo;hitched his wagon&rdquo; to Trump and <span class=\"red\">felt he was answering a &ldquo;call&rdquo; from the president to go there</span> (阿侵叫我黎架).<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ca-times.brightspotcdn.com/dims4/default/ed97d99/2147483647/strip/true/crop/6000x4000+0+0/resize/840x560!/quality/90/?url=https%3A%2F%2Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fbf%2F0c%2F8cd82ac6882dc8bd87861ba52355%2Fb8aa6b0b81c2407e99bb61e95a9e4331\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fca-times.brightspotcdn.com%2Fdims4%2Fdefault%2Fed97d99%2F2147483647%2Fstrip%2Ftrue%2Fcrop%2F6000x4000%2B0%2B0%2Fresize%2F840x560%21%2Fquality%2F90%2F%3Furl%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fcalifornia-times-brightspot.s3.amazonaws.com%252Fbf%252F0c%252F8cd82ac6882dc8bd87861ba52355%252Fb8aa6b0b81c2407e99bb61e95a9e4331&h=c0393e97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;The words and invitation of a president are supposed to mean something (你係總統唔撚係當我地係condom 啊),&rdquo; said the attorney, Albert Watkins.<br />\n<br />\n​source: <a href=\"https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2021-01-17/alleged-capitol-rioters-argue-they-were-invited-into-the-building-by-trump-seek-pardons\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fpolitics%2Fstory%2F2021-01-17%2Falleged-capitol-rioters-argue-they-were-invited-into-the-building-by-trump-seek-pardons&d=nfq7Ayl5XWctTRRkLGDCS%2BdgoykoOisTuuABwIAScok%3D&h=b89e4b96\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.latimes.com/politics/story/2021-01-17/alleged-capitol-rioters-argue-they-were-invited-into-the-building-by-trump-seek-pardons</a>"},{"pid":"3e013432daa32b21dd244ec1a34d101040093114","tid":2370182,"uid":105798,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T22:05:00.000Z","msg":"樓主講野有鄉音<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23ca011695dd361c642298656de3f646b99eab8c","tid":2370182,"uid":105798,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T22:06:41.000Z","msg":"學人唔戴罩啊拿<br />\nmasks don't work 啊拿<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c312cd064e2502677efb49f302814dfbe1d0af41","tid":2370182,"uid":105798,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-17T22:08:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.pennlive.com/resizer/iSf8EHsUYy6oKwJIR_XwoVOi9V8=/1280x0/smart/cloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com/advancelocal/I2AROB3BH5CSVNATLPJFN7BUMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pennlive.com%2Fresizer%2FiSf8EHsUYy6oKwJIR_XwoVOi9V8%3D%2F1280x0%2Fsmart%2Fcloudfront-us-east-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fadvancelocal%2FI2AROB3BH5CSVNATLPJFN7BUMA.jpg&h=b9